title: Live From Austin!
description:
Our first RISK! live show in the city that keeps it weird, Austin, Texas.

Support RISK! on Patreon at Patreon.com/RISK

author: Kevin@RISK-show.com (Nick Scott, Dhaya Lakshminarayanan, Michael Jastroch, Fleet Foxes, Sam Dingman, Paul Normandin, Kevin Allison, Shawn Lee)
